  "intro": "Zazaa Ganbold is a Mongolian born contemporary artist working across Germany, Portugal and Mongolia. Her practice spans painting, mixed media, digital works and drawing. Through layered symbolic imagery, she explores the human body as a site of memory, transformation and inner consciousness.",
