    "1994 to 1999, Bachelor of Arts in Painting and Graphic Design, Mongolian University of Arts and Culture, Ulaanbaatar.",
    "2000 to 2002, Independent research travels to China, Korea, Japan and India, focusing on contemporary art and traditional Asian cultural practices."
  ],
